OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776902565
OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries in north
OL,4,CBelfast attack
OL,6,FPolice are appealing for information
OL,7,Ffollowing an assault in the Ardoyne
OL,8,FRoad area of north Belfast.
OL,10,FDetective Sergeant Faulkner said:
OL,11,F"Shortly after 11:30pm on Monday 20th
OL,12,FApril, it was reported that a man in
OL,13,Fhis 30s was walking in the area when a
OL,14,Fsilver Volkswagen Polo car pulled up
OL,15,Fbeside him.
OL,17,F"Three men armed with weapons
OL,18,Fincluding a claw hammer and a metal
OL,19,Fbat exited the vehicle and assaulted
OL,20,Fthe male.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
