OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776902565
OL,3,CMan suffers serious injuries in north
OL,4,CBelfast attack
OL,6,F"The men then made off in the vehicle
OL,7,Ffollowing the incident. One of the
OL,8,Fmales involved is described as being
OL,9,Fof heavy build wearing a dark coloured
OL,10,Fmask.
OL,12,F"The man received fractures and
OL,13,Flacerations following the assault and
OL,14,Fwas treated in hospital for his
OL,15,Finjuries."
OL,17,FPolice have said that enquiries are
OL,18,Fcontinuing and would appeal to anyone
OL,19,Fwith any information to contact them
OL,20,Fon 101 quoting reference number 1440
OL,21,F21/04/26.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
